      <title>特朗普时代寻求稳定的投资者选择南非</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/why-south-africa-could-lead-emerging-markets-under-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长期以来，南非一直被冠以动荡和高风险的新兴市场的称号，但现在，在唐纳德·特朗普担任美国总统的背景下，南非正成为投资者的最爱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/why-south-africa-could-lead-emerging-markets-under-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
